  "storyboard_markdown": "# Scene Contract: CH011_SC003\n\n## Production Intent\nEstablish the overwhelming scale of the Wizard's manifestation to trigger a shift from fear to determination in Dorothy. The visual hierarchy must emphasize the disparity between a small human girl and a giant, disembodied head within the palace architecture.\n\n## Required Cast\n- dorothy (young human girl, weary traveler, white dress)\n- toto (small dog)\n- the_great_oz (Giant Head manifestation)\n\n## Required Environments\n- palace_of_oz (Audience Chamber/Throne Room)\n\n## Continuity Constraints\n- Scale relationship between the_great_oz and dorothy must remain consistent across coverage.\n- Dorothy's clothing must reflect her status as a weary traveler in white.\n\n## Beat List\n- BT001: Dorothy enters the audience chamber.\n- BT002: The manifestation of the Wizard (Giant Head).\n- BT003: The ultimatum is delivered (Kill the Wicked Witch to return home).",
